*Why did I receive this email?*

    You have a <%= AppConfig.name %> account at <<%= AppConfig.base_url %>>. This email message was sent automatically to notify you<%= @why %>.

*How can I unsubscribe?*

    These email notifications will be sent to you automatically as long as you have an account with <%= AppConfig.name %>. You can delete your account by going to your My Profile page at <<%= AppConfig.base_url %>my/profile>, logging in, and clicking the Delete link.

*Where can I get more information?*

    You can find more information about <%= AppConfig.name %> on our About page at <<%= AppConfig.base_url %>about>. You can read our full privacy policy (including our commitment to sending you only pertinent emails, and to guard your email address) on our Privacy Policy page at <<%= AppConfig.base_url %>privacy>.

*Who can I ask if I have further questions?*

    You can contact the <%= AppConfig.name %> team by sending an email to <<%= AppConfig.contact_email %>>.
